# Clearance Level 3

The following document lists all duties of command

If you are not of security clearance level 3, please dispose of this document and report its existance to the NTR

# Nanotrasen Representative

[bold]1.[/bold] The Nanotrasen Representative is expected to follow all orders from central command;

[bold]2.[/bold] The Nanotrasen Representative is expected to ensure command is following all orders from Central Command;

[bold]3.[/bold] If the orders are not followed, the Nanotrasen Representative is expected to eliminate said command member;

# Blue Shield Officer

[bold]1.[/bold] The Blue Shield Officer is expected to protect all members of command to a reasonable extent;

[bold]2.[/bold] The Blue Shield Officer is expected to protect the Nanotrasen Representative with their life;

[bold]3.[/bold] The Blue Shield Officer is expected to follow orders from the Nanotrasen Representative;

[bold]4.[/bold] The Blue Shield Officer is expected to assist the captain in eliminating any anti-Nanotrasen sympathies;
